 rising star boyfriend."],[2435,2527,"What could be better?"],[2527,2619,"Exactly."],[2656,2819,"We can't wait to learn from you guys."],[2857,3090,"Aw, thank you."],[3090,3215,"I mean, with your skills,"],[3215,3353,"you probably got the head chef slots"],[3353,3440,"on lock already."],[3440,3503,"Oh, yeah."],[3503,3574,"I heard there's some"],[3574,3687,"mysterious heavy hitter"],[3687,3862,"serving as the Head Qualifying Judge."],[3920,4045,"Any idea who it is?"],[4066,4141,"Whoever it is,"],[4141,4195,"they are going to"],[4195,4325,"bow down to my cooking."],[6043,6139,"What are they doing here?"]],"49":[[50,150,"What are they doing here?"],[254,400,"Family sponsor perks."],[417,588,"They don't actually deserve to be here."],[621,754,"Using your husband's family name"],[754,905,"to get a spot at this training?"],[959,1126,"You even show up wearing that coat?"],[1167,1388,"Do yourself a favor and go take it off."],[1388,1463,"She's right."],[1468,1580,"Just leave, Tiffany."],[1614,1810,"The chief advisor is about to arrive."],[1835,1885,"You don't want to"],[1885,2068,"make your husband's family look bad."],[2498,2623,"They have zero idea that"],[2623,2798,"I'm the chief advisor."],[3019,3140,"Tiffany, I need to speak with you."],[3174,3253,"Can you come with me?"],[5613,5801,"I don't have time for your nonsense."],[5880,6010,"And in case you forgot,"],[6010,6126,"we're divorced."],[6206,6373,"Stay away from me."],[7094,7140,"I don't believe"],[7140,7294,"that you could just move on like that."]],"50":[[150,291,"Let go."],[1005,1197,"Step away from my wife."],[1288,1368,"Mr. Wyndham,"],[1368,1530,"I just want a word with my ex-wife."],[1572,1664,"Should just take a moment."],[1693,1793,"Save it, Barry."],[1818,1968,"You weren't a good husband to me"],[1993,2097,"and you're not a good husband"],[2097,2168,"to anyone now."],[2273,2356,"We're divorced."],[2381,2540,"Stop bothering me."],[2652,2748,"Did you hear my wife?"],[2802,2911,"Stay away from her."],[4112,4208,"What the fuck?"],[5226,5351,"This has to be a mistake."]],"51":[[116,262,"You gotta be fucking kidding me."],[271,425,"You can't just pull shit like that."],[446,583,"Who messed with the positions?"],[671,721,"What?"],[1401,1472,"Was it you?"],[1576,1714,"Don't try to pin this on me."],[1776,1881,"I didn't lift a finger."],[1901,2060,"This guy thinks his sponsor status"],[2060,2185,"gives him total impunity."],[2185,2318,"Fucking shameless."],[2335,2414,"Get them out."],[2435,2544,"Yeah, get them out!"],[2581,2706,"Get them out."],[2723,2831,"Get them out."],[2852,2957,"Get them out."],[2969,3086,"Get them out."],[3098,3211,"Get them out."],[3224,3340,"Get them out."],[3357,3470,"Get them out."],[3474,3595,"Get them out."],[3603,3707,"Get them out."],[3712,3770,"Get them out."],[3770,3828,"Quiet!"],[4270,4387,"That's Michelle Jones."],[4421,4550,"One of the top judges"],[4550,4675,"in the culinary world."]],"52":[[229,316,"Ms. Jones,"],[367,462,"there's someone here"],[462,621,"impersonating a Qualifying Judge."],[650,725,"Move."],[892,1046,"I apologize for the delay,"],[1046,1134,"Mrs. Wyndham."],[1176,1334,"No, you're right on time."],[1359,1434,"Ms. Jones, they're not"],[1434,1543,"even supposed to be here."],[1714,1776,"Attention."],[1922,2189,"Tiffany Wyndham is not a contestant."],[2223,2452,"She is not here to compete with you all."],[2552,2815,"Tiffany is beyond qualification."],[2998,3086,"Which is why"],[3086,3332,"she is the Head Qualifying Judge"],[3332,3536,"of the entire competition."],[3620,3787,"And will decide which one of you"],[3787,3978,"advances to the next level."],[4054,4104,"What?"],[4108,4195,"Impossible."],[4216,4387,"Why would they select a housewife?"],[4416,4625,"But that's Mr. Dunlap's signature."],[4688,4808,"That can't be fake."],[5238,5409,"Was I blind this whole time?"],[5409,5568,"Did I ever really know her?"]],"53":[[54,175,"Thank you, Mrs. Jones."],[400,504,"As you've all heard,"],[504,633,"I'm the Head Qualifying Judge"],[633,746,"of this competition."],[817,1017,"I'll be presiding over the contenders,"],[1017,1188,"evaluating your skills,"],[1209,1393,"and deciding who advances."],[1413,1534,"All requirements will be set"],[1534,1718,"according to my personal standards"],[1718,1839,"and stipulations."],[1872,2002,"No exceptions."],[2118,2210,"She wants clout."],[2243,2352,"Why not just get the Wyndham"],[2352,2510,"to get a spot with her name on it?"],[2510,2610,"That way she wouldn't have to"],[2610,2719,"ruin this competition."],[2756,2927,"Chef Sera was right on the money."],[3007,3174,"She slept her way into this."],[3182,3274,"Just some divorced chick"],[3274,3457,"who knows nothing about real cooking."],[3474,3595,"Yeah, why should"],[3595,3741,"a bunch of professional chefs"],[3741,3849,"take orders from her?"],[3849,3945,"It's ridiculous."],[4008,4133,"Sera's a real chef,"],[4166,4350,"the Queen of Cuisine's protégé."],[4404,4475,"But we're supposed to"],[4475,4596,"answer to some housewife"],[4596,4688,"riding the Wyndham's"],[4688,4746,"coattails?"],[4804,4900,"This is insulting."]],"54":[[0,100,"This is insulting."],[1113,1222,"If you have a problem,"],[1247,1372,"the exit's right over there."],[1976,2064,"That's what I thought."],[2740,2865,"I hope the Queen of Cuisine"],[2865,2965,"taught you well, Sera."],[3015,3123,"You're going to need it."],[4029,4116,"They want to put that whore"],[4116,4233,"of a housewife above me?"],[4308,4408,"Outrageous."],[4466,4629,"Just forget her, Sera, okay?"],[4671,4800,"Focus on training."],[4846,4950,"I have an idea."],[4984,5050,"What are you doing?"],[5050,5121,"I'm challenging her."],[5121,5205,"I'm gonna get her"],[5205,5526,"to drop this fake head chef act."],[5551,5672,"And then I'm going to expose her"],[5672,5843,"in front of everyone as being a fraud."],[5914,6060,"Don't be rash. Ok?"],[6060,6227,"Tiffany's not just some pushover."],[6281,6452,"Relax, I know what I'm doing."]],"55":[[396,471,"Mr. Dunlap."],[700,796,"I'm filing a complaint."],[796,896,"Tiffany has no right"],[896,992,"to be at this training."],[1026,1159,"Mr. Dunlap isn't here"],[1159,1284,"to listen to your ranting."],[1305,1384,"But it's not fair."],[1384,1480,"She just wormed her way"],[1480,1597,"into the Wyndham family."],[1618,1697,"How can she be"],[1697,1847,"the Head Qualifying Judge?"],[1847,1989,"This event is rigged."],[1989,2056,"You think you can just"],[2056,2139,"spread some rumors"],[2139,2256,"and get her to stand down?"],[2256,2502,"The fact she's here proves her ability."],[2656,2715,"And also,"],[2715,2857,"I'm not just going to stand back"],[2857,3023,"and watch you insult my wife."],[3103,3211,"It's all good, brother."],[3853,3995,"Of course you're defending her."],[4033,4129,"He's the husband."],[4208,4312,"That's right."],[4479,4571,"It's not fair."],[4646,4909,"Head Qualifying Judge is appointed"],[4942,5146,"by the Culinary Institute of America"],[5180,5426,"based on experience and merit."],[5497,5709,"And Chef Tiffany is more than qualified."],[5739,5805,"Now, if you want"],[5805,6047,"a national banquet head chef slot,"],[6047,6231,"you'll need to follow her directions."],[6268,6460,"No, I'm protesting the selection."],[6481,6656,"If we're judging based off of skill,"],[6656,6819,"I should be the Qualifying Judge."],[6856,7007,"I formally challenge Tiffany"],[7007,7127,"to a culinary duel."],[7165,7248,"I'll prove to everyone"],[7248,7340,"that she doesn't belong."]],"56":[[216,475,"No, the banquet is fast approaching."],[492,621,"You chefs need to be working"],[621,717,"on your craft."],[767,850,"And besides,"],[1034,1134,"challenging Tiffany"],[1134,1259,"is not a bright idea."],[1313,1401,"What's wrong?"],[1401,1459,"Afraid I'm gonna"],[1459,1576,"embarrass that housewife?"],[1643,1780,"Or that people will question"],[1780,1856,"your decision?"],[1889,1976,"Chef Sera,"],[1976,2181,"cheap taunts don't work on me."],[2227,2310,"Put her on stage."],[2310,2427,"Let's see what she's got."],[2427,2535,"Yeah!"],[2594,2731,"Make her accept the challenge."],[2748,2911,"Otherwise, we won't accept her."],[2944,3019,"Yeah. - Yeah."],[3082,3136,"See?"],[3144,3265,"No one's convinced."],[3324,3461,"The press would be interested to know"],[3461,3570,"why award-winning chefs"],[3570,3728,"walked after you appointed"],[3728,3862,"an unknown judge."],[3924,4041,"I wonder what they'll assume."]],"57":[[191,316,"Sure, you can challenge her."],[367,462,"But if you lose,"],[525,704,"you'll have a one-year suspension."],[713,896,"You'll be stripped of your titles."],[930,1030,"You won't be in the running"],[1030,1117,"for head chef."],[1117,1213,"That's not fair."],[1213,1292,"If Tiffany loses,"],[1292,1434,"she doesn't get in trouble at all."],[1434,1505,"But if I lose,"],[1505,1614,"I'm suspended for a year?"],[1655,1714,"Wrong."],[1739,1835,"If Tiffany loses,"],[1835,2002,"your accusations will stick."],[2039,2223,"She'll be out of the culinary industry."],[2260,2410,"Don't pretend that there's no cost."],[2435,2631,"One-year suspension is too severe."],[2631,2798,"You're the one challenging her"],[2798,2986,"to settle a petty personal score."],[3023,3148,"But it's not just that."],[3253,3365,"Challenging Tiffany"],[3365,3482,"means challenging me."],[3666,3845,"I... I, um..."],[3849,3995,"What happened to all that swagger?"],[4037,4083,"You're getting"],[4083,4220,"special treatment, Sera."],[4220,4295,"If everyone here"],[4295,4450,"questioned Mr. Dunlap like you,"],[4487,4671,"this training camp would be a disaster."],[4750,4829,"Relax."],[4829,4929,"You won't lose."],[4929,5063,"You were born a winner."],[5063,5196,"Mr. Dunlap's just bluffing"],[5196,5284,"to scare me off."],[5342,5472,"She's a freaking housewife."],[5488,5622,"I'm gonna eviscerate her."],[5651,5705,"Fine."],[5730,5797,"Bring it on."],[5847,5901,"Tomorrow?"],[6177,6235,"Fine."],[6235,6368,"I'll be at a White House dinner."],[6368,6585,"But I'll have a cadre of expert chefs"],[6610,6802,"watching you and Tiffany compete."]],"58":[[179,362,"Everybody, back to work!"],[1017,1117,"You seem pretty confident"],[1117,1201,"about Tiffany."],[1372,1434,"I am."],[1518,1593,"She's going to win."],[1876,2035,"If Sera wants to bring the heat,"],[2068,2198,"Tiffany will bring the fire."],[2727,2806,"Sera, why'd you let them"],[2806,2923,"raise the stakes so high?"],[3028,3157,"Tiffany's really good."],[3157,3286,"I already lost to her."],[3286,3449,"This just feels reckless."],[3482,3641,"I'm not being reckless."],[3682,3799,"I'm going to punish that fraud"],[3799,3962,"and expose her scandal."],[4004,4083,"And besides,"],[4083,4266,"this will help our head chef campaign."],[4287,4408,"But if you lose,"],[4408,4533,"you're kicked out of the industry"],[4533,4600,"for a year."],[4629,4775,"And our head chef shot is gone."],[4859,4979,"You underestimate me."],[5021,5130,"I won't lose."],[5188,5347,"Sera, if you lose tomorrow,"],[5388,5488,"you'll have nothing."],[5605,5743,"You'll never be able to show your face"],[5743,5864,"in the Culinary World again."],[5889,6001,"Are you willing to stay home"],[6001,6093,"and be a housewife"],[6093,6177,"if that happens?"],[6285,6473,"If it means being your housewife,"],[6527,6685,"I am more than willing."],[7403,7507,"I'm not losing."],[7832,7987,"And I'm never going to be"],[7987,8128,"a fucking housewife."]],"59":[[629,921,"And now, introducing our special judges!"],[1088,1217,"It's Ms. Jones."],[1739,1960,"World-class judge Andre Lorenzo?"],[1993,2181,"And famed critic Iris Lee?"],[2293,2389,"That's a heavyweight panel"],[2389,2489,"if I've ever seen one."],[2631,2777,"They're obviously here for Chef Sera."],[2815,2852,"You know"],[2852,2990,"she's the Queen of Cuisine's protégé."],[2998,3174,"She's gonna receive her coronation"],[3174,3261,"and get her crown."],[3349,3411,"Is that..."],[5326,5459,"That's Leon Kennedy,"],[5522,5638,"the King of Cooking!"]],"60":[[533,608,"I would like to"],[608,796,"thank our esteemed judges"],[796,1021,"for coming here at such short notice."],[1151,1497,"Today, Chef Sera and Chef Tiffany"],[1530,1689,"will put their skills to test."],[1714,1860,"Colleagues, this competition"],[1860,2014,"should showcase the best of us."],[2052,2177,"But a talentless castoff"],[2177,2260,"has wormed her way in"],[2260,2398,"by getting close to the rich."],[2452,2565,"Today, I'm exposing her."],[2644,2736,"It's unfair."],[2773,2869,"We work our tails off,"],[2869,2957,"day in and day out,"],[2957,3048,"just to be here."],[3048,3132,"And she steps in"],[3132,3282,"because of one little connection."],[3282,3445,"It's an insult to our craft."],[3486,3691,"Chef Sera, we're rooting for you."],[3691,3741,"Beat her"],[3741,3874,"and kick her out of the culinary world."],[3912,3999,"Look around."],[4029,4133,"Everyone's here for me."],[4187,4304,"You're going down, Tiffany."],[4542,4688,"Yeah, kick her out!"],[4688,4813,"Kick her out!"],[4833,4938,"Kick her out!"],[4954,5430,"Kick her out!"],[5430,5547,"What now, bitch?"]],"61":[[0,483,"Kick her out!"],[679,863,"Chefs, this competition"],[863,1096,"is about value and honor."],[1134,1251,"I expect everyone here"],[1251,1359,"to conduct themselves"],[1359,1443,"accordingly."],[1505,1714,"Judges, I will leave it to you."],[2727,2952,"Ladies, it's time to drop"],[2952,3094,"any pre-existing grudges"],[3094,3299,"and let skill settle the truth."],[3324,3415,"My grudge doesn't drop"],[3415,3528,"until I avenge Barry."],[3649,3778,"He says your knife work is decent,"],[3778,3870,"so let's start there."],[4141,4208,"Fine."],[4437,4537,"Slice a potato"],[4537,4754,"into the thinnest possible ribbons."],[4796,4909,"The thinnest one wins."],[5021,5080,"Begin."]],"62":[[5626,5697,"Look!"],[5755,5822,"That's..."],[6089,6193,"That's my move."],[8458,8591,"What the hell are you doing?"],[8629,8742,"You've been cutting forever"],[8742,8863,"and your potato's still whole."]],"63":[[5217,5392,"Tiffany's potatoes are paper-thin."],[5588,5759,"I declare her the winner"],[5759,5897,"of the knife work competition."],[6902,7061,"No, I won't accept this."],[7061,7152,"She's just getting away"],[7152,7282,"with cheap tricks."],[7482,7611,"I challenge you to a cooking duel."],[7657,7711,"Deal."],[7732,7849,"I can do this all day,"],[7882,8049,"until you're begging me for mercy."]],"64":[[4,83,"Your challenge,"],[154,241,"cook a main course"],[241,471,"from past National Banquet menus."],[588,638,"Iris."],[1664,1810,"I choose the Beef Wellington."],[2031,2164,"That's right Sera!"],[2189,2394,"Tiffany can't beat you with that dish!"],[2439,2669,"I choose the Dover Sole."],[3103,3174,"Good luck."],[3257,3324,"Really?"],[3395,3445,"Fish?"],[3445,3549,"What a freaking cop-out."],[3549,3716,"It's actually harder than you think."],[3720,3812,"It doesn't matter."],[3812,3953,"Just because she won the first round,"],[3953,4058,"it doesn't mean she's gonna"],[4058,4183,"win the entire competition."],[4183,4300,"Yeah, she looks like she's cheating."],[4617,4804,"Now, Dover Sole may look simple,"],[4842,4913,"but the real test"],[4913,5038,"is gonna be the mushroom pairing."],[5055,5230,"Balancing the fish and mushrooms"],[5230,5355,"is no walk in the park."],[5355,5476,"The two can easily"],[5476,5580,"overwhelm each other."],[5580,5755,"And because the heat control"],[5755,5972,"requires great precision."],[5972,6101,"It's only appeared once"],[6101,6293,"on a past National Banquet menu."],[6293,6464,"It's actually a dish"],[6464,6602,"many head chefs fear."],[6681,6802,"You didn't know that, did you?"],[6831,7002,"You tried to take the easy way out,"],[7002,7257,"and you stumbled into the hardest dish."],[7365,7503,"You'll see soon enough."]],"65":[[0,375,"Chef Sera, Chef Tiffany, begin."],[4808,5005,"Dude, that steamer can set"],[5005,5113,"the temperature for her."],[5113,5196,"How's that cooking?"],[5196,5342,"A freaking caveman can do it."],[5434,5568,"Fuckin' peanut brain."]],"66":[[3661,3737,"Interesting."],[3753,3941,"She's ditching the precision machine"],[3941,4099,"and going back to fundamentals."],[4358,4454,"If Sera loses,"],[4454,4583,"she's suspended for a year"],[4583,4750,"and out of the head-chef race."],[6268,6331,"Sera!"],[6439,6585,"Don't underestimate her."],[6702,6856,"This bitch thinks she's hot shit"],[6856,6994,"because she lucked out and beat you."],[7048,7115,"Don't worry."],[7532,7678,"I'm going to cut her down to size."]],"67":[[4350,4550,"That steam was made specially"],[4550,4658,"for beasts like you."],[5259,5347,"My dish..."],[5784,5922,"White Knight's Soul."]],"68":[[1518,1601,"You think a fish"],[1601,1710,"made with home cookware"],[1710,1785,"stands a chance"],[1785,1931,"next to my Beef Wellington?"],[1989,2072,"Keep dreaming."],[2143,2235,"The National Banquet"],[2235,2352,"needs top chefs,"],[2381,2535,"not housewives in aprons."],[3891,4099,"I knew she would blow it."],[4587,4688,"Oh my goodness."],[4767,4879,"Leon, you were right."],[5213,5476,"The flavor, that burst that just"],[5513,5684,"gets sent down your spine."],[5705,5872,"Only the Queen of Cuisine"],[5872,6001,"could do something like this."],[6310,6410,"What does she mean,"],[6410,6531,"Queen of Cuisine?"],[6531,6702,"She means Chef Sera's the winner."],[6702,6840,"She's the Queen's protégé."],[6848,7002,"Only she can cook at that level."],[7165,7261,"That's right bitch."],[7303,7432,"You will never win."]],"69":[[0,150,"The decision is unanimous."],[150,358,"Only the Queen of Cuisine herself"],[421,575,"could craft the winning dish."],[934,1030,"The winner is..."],[2206,2298,"Chef Tiffany."],[3474,3536,"What?"],[3674,3962,"She's the long lost Queen of Cuisine?"],[4004,4074,"No, it's impossible."],[4074,4149,"There's no way."],[5568,5643,"Correct."],[5705,5864,"I am the Queen of Cuisine,"],[5905,6106,"back after a three-year hiatus."],[6314,6527,"You called me a lowly housewife,"],[6564,6773,"a woman who clings to the rich."],[6802,7098,"But who I truly am, is Tiffany Lockhart."],[7173,7386,"The Queen of Cuisine."]],"70":[[50,158,"Nice try, liar!"],[179,300,"That fish is home cooking"],[300,383,"nothing more."],[417,508,"You were barely even able to"],[508,675,"flip pancakes for my husband."],[709,759,"Sera."],[825,938,"You heard the results."],[1067,1205,"And as agreed,"],[1205,1309,"you are now removed"],[1309,1443,"from this training camp"],[1484,1614,"and suspended for one year."],[1651,1735,"You and your husband"],[1735,1856,"will also lose eligibility"],[1856,2060,"for this banquet's head chef selection."],[2473,2540,"Sera."],[2565,2615,"Barry, no."],[2615,2765,"She's just a housewife, okay?"],[2781,2869,"She's been propped up"],[2869,3007,"by Wyndham family money."],[3028,3311,"I told you not to underestimate her."],[3503,3574,"This is rigged."],[3574,3653,"Open your eyes."],[3653,3737,"This whole event has been"],[3737,3866,"fixed from the start."],[3866,4016,"Yeah, didn't the Queen of Cuisine"],[4016,4154,"retire like three years ago?"],[4154,4279,"She's an imposter."],[5009,5059,"That's enough."],[5455,5551,"You didn't lose"],[5551,5689,"because of money or power."],[5918,6018,"You lost"],[6081,6151,"because your cooking"],[6151,6272,"can't hold a torch"],[6343,6485,"to the Queen of Cuisine's."]],"71":[[83,200,"The Queen of Cuisine?"],[233,367,"The real Queen of Cuisine"],[367,496,"wouldn't be some tramp"],[496,592,"who married into money"],[592,825,"after getting dumped by her ex-husband."],[1009,1096,"She's trash."],[1134,1247,"Drop the act."],[1255,1413,"You're a slutty social climber"],[1413,1576,"in a chef's coat."],[1906,2072,"Real chefs speak through food,"],[2072,2210,"not rumor and envy."],[2231,2448,"Stop disgracing our craft."],[2648,2786,"People, are you really"],[2786,2898,"going to believe this?"],[2907,2977,"Are you going to"],[2977,3186,"let her shove this power"],[3186,3286,"down your throats?"],[3303,3445,"This isn't cooking."],[3470,3632,"It's a goddamn travesty."],[3724,3791,"That's right."],[3828,3941,"She got here through connections,"],[3941,4008,"not merit."],[4008,4129,"This shit's rigged."],[4179,4291,"Totally rigged!"],[4429,4750,"Rigged!"],[4758,5055,"Rigged!"],[5067,5330,"Rigged!"],[5338,5601,"Rigged!"],[5605,5864,"Rigged!"],[5868,6131,"Rigged!"],[6143,6598,"Rigged!"],[7399,7474,"Liam."],[7503,7615,"Liam, can you hear me?"],[7736,7820,"If you still want me"],[7820,7957,"to lead this year's national banquet"],[7957,8053,"at the White House,"],[8053,8254,"I need you here in five minutes or less."]],"72":[[171,279,"Huh, just trying to flex?"],[316,442,"Don't you even read the news?"],[462,604,"Liam Dunlap's at the White House"],[604,675,"right now."],[696,754,"Oh you think you're gonna"],[754,871,"pull him away from the White House"],[871,1001,"with one lousy phone call?"],[1051,1159,"What, are you a comedian too?"],[1159,1317,"The Wyndhams are powerful,"],[1317,1393,"but they're nothing"],[1393,1543,"compared to the White House."],[1551,1659,"Apologize now"],[1659,1751,"or you will never"],[1751,1893,"work in this industry again."],[1964,2014,"Fine."],[2060,2189,"Since you gave us such a good laugh,"],[2189,2318,"I'll give you a chance."],[2339,2489,"Admit you're an imposter"],[2489,2640,"and leave with some dignity."],[2681,2811,"Admit you're just a housewife."],[3032,3169,"You're beyond saving."],[3169,3345,"You're the one who needs saving, bitch."],[3912,3978,"Three..."],[4124,4200,"Still playing tough?"],[4200,4254,"Two..."],[4708,4767,"One."],[5626,5697,"It's the president"],[5697,5818,"of the Culinary Institute,"],[5868,5951,"Liam Dunlap."]],"73":[[108,175,"Leon."],[229,275,"Liam."],[300,433,"Mr. Dunlap, I thought you were"],[433,533,"at the White House."],[558,658,"Indeed I was."],[692,859,"And then I received an urgent call."],[925,988,"What's going on?"],[1030,1101,"Mr. Dunlap,"],[1101,1180,"I challenged Tiffany"],[1180,1292,"just like we agreed upon,"],[1292,1468,"but the Wyndhams bought the judges"],[1468,1572,"and rigged the results."],[1931,2047,"I thought this competition"],[2047,2135,"would sober you."],[2202,2264,"But it looks like"],[2264,2373,"you're just doubling down"],[2373,2531,"on all your worst impulses."],[2590,2669,"What do you mean?"],[2669,2831,"This bitch is just a housewife."],[2852,2948,"And besides,"],[2948,3111,"she's claiming to be"],[3111,3253,"the Queen of Cuisine."],[3274,3378,"You fool."],[3440,3611,"She is the Queen of Cuisine."],[3845,3933,"Three years ago,"],[3949,4124,"she sacrificed her career"],[4124,4241,"for her then-husband"],[4270,4433,"and became a stay-at-home wife."],[4491,4667,"And because of your provocation,"],[5226,5605,"she now is reclaiming her rightful place"],[5605,5684,"on the throne."],[9146,9242,"I knew it."],[9317,9613,"Tiffany is the Queen of Cuisine after all."],[9680,9897,"She was my idol all along?"],[10130,10447,"Tiffany is the Queen of Cuisine?"]],"74":[[87,246,"I threw the Queen of Cuisine away"],[246,346,"for Sera?"],[383,450,"Fuck you."],[492,713,"Tiffany, I'm sorry."],[759,888,"Had I foreseen this,"],[946,1084,"I would have never signed off"],[1084,1192,"on the challenge."],[1455,1543,"And you two,"],[1568,1672,"effective immediately,"],[1672,1780,"you're blacklisted."],[1801,1985,"You'll never work as chefs again."],[2081,2210,"Tiffany, Tiffany,"],[2210,2323,"I, I didn't know that you were"],[2323,2398,"the Queen of Cuisine."],[2398,2460,"Okay, I..."],[2494,2627,"But this wasn't my idea."],[2627,2723,"It was Sera's."],[2756,2861,"She started the challenge,"],[2861,2923,"picked the fight,"],[2923,3028,"she spread the rumors."],[3057,3148,"I am innocent."],[3148,3257,"Barry? Babe, what are you doing?"],[3257,3319,"You're my husband."],[3319,3449,"Not anymore I'm not!"],[3449,3607,"Stop trying to drag me down with you."],[3807,3937,"With Tiffany by my side,"],[3991,4149,"the sky is our limit."],[4237,4483,"She is my real wife."],[4821,4946,"In your dreams, pal."],[5000,5113,"You really still have the nerve"],[5113,5246,"to call me your wife?"],[5267,5488,"Tiffany, Tiffany, come on, please."],[5534,5609,"Please, you,"],[5609,5830,"you did all this to show me, okay?"],[5830,5939,"You showed me my mistakes"],[5939,6031,"and I see them."],[6068,6231,"I can take you back, okay?"],[6231,6306,"I can."],[6327,6385,"I don't even care"],[6385,6485,"that you got remarried."],[7248,7424,"I am not your wife."],[7490,7653,"I'm not wasting another second"],[7653,7782,"living in your shadow."],[7932,8103,"I'm Tiffany Wyndham..."],[8170,8312,"Queen of Cuisine."]],"75":[[25,171,"Please, please, please, please."],[171,237,"please, please."],[258,379,"For the sake of everything we had,"],[379,667,"all I ask is that you let me stay"],[667,771,"in the industry."],[909,1076,"Please, please, please,"],[1117,1222,"please, please."],[2752,2911,"Keeping you in the Culinary World"],[2911,3003,"would be an insult"],[3003,3123,"to the art of cooking."],[3386,3465,"Get out."],[3578,3649,"No!"],[3716,3812,"No!"],[3832,3920,"You're no queen."],[4141,4316,"You're a damn whore."]],"76":[[487,613,"You'll never beat me."],[650,804,"Not because you're weak,"],[829,880,"but because you're"],[880,1009,"small-minded and petty."],[1059,1209,"From this day forward,"],[1217,1338,"you have no right"],[1338,1480,"to stand in any kitchen."],[1605,1856,"Now take your sorry excuse of a man"],[1876,1960,"and get out."],[1981,2177,"Security, get these two out of here."],[2235,2285,"No!"],[2293,2339,"No!"],[2381,2456,"No!"],[3040,3461,"Tiffany, please return as head chef"],[3461,3636,"for this year's national banquet."],[3749,3924,"We need you to lead us."],[3924,4208,"Queen of Cuisine, please lead us."],[4208,4304,"Please lead us."],[4325,4396,"Please lead us."],[4404,4504,"Please lead us."],[4512,4675,"Please lead us."],[4708,4859,"Queen of Cuisine."],[4896,5030,"Queen of Cuisine."],[5071,5221,"Queen of Cuisine."],[5251,5718,"Queen of Cuisine."],[5739,6210,"Queen of Cuisine."],[6231,6819,"Queen of Cuisine."],[6840,7553,"Queen of Cuisine."]],"77":[[625,792,"Now, I know you're the one"],[792,917,"who's usually stunning people"],[917,1042,"with your cooking, but..."],[1172,1234,"tonight..."],[1543,1605,"it's my turn."],[2327,2406,"Looks like someone"],[2406,2489,"wants to be my knight"],[2489,2590,"in shining armor."],[2752,2873,"I hope more than just that."],[3073,3186,"Tiffany, you taught me"],[3186,3311,"how to use cooking"],[3311,3495,"to express what words can't."],[3566,3707,"So, tonight,"],[4066,4225,"whether you're the Queen of Cuisine"],[4337,4529,"or just the kind and beautiful woman"],[4629,4729,"that I've gotten to know,"],[4833,4967,"I want to be your husband."],[5889,5951,"Yes."],[6006,6068,"Yes!"]]}